'''荷西·里安納度·紐尼斯·艾維斯·蘇沙·渣甸'''（{{lang-pt|José Leonardo Nunes Alves Sousa Jardim}}，{{IPA-pt|liuˈnaɾdu ʒɐɾˈdĩ}}，{{bd|1974年|8月1日}}），葡萄牙足球領隊，曾執教[[法甲|法甲]]球會{{fc|摩納哥}}。

==足球生涯==
渣甸出生於[[委內瑞拉|委內瑞拉]][[巴塞羅那_(安索阿特吉州)|巴塞隆拿]]，父母在當地停留時誕下他。渣甸在出生不久便返回葡萄牙，居住於[[馬德拉島|馬德拉島]]。2001年，年僅27歲的他展開其領隊生涯，在本土球會{{scl|卡馬查}}擔任兩年助教。

其後，渣甸獲得該[[葡丙|葡丙]]球會擢昇為主教練，並在2007/08球季中段轉投另一支球會{{scl|查維斯}}，並帶領該支球會從[[葡乙|葡乙]]升班至[[葡甲|葡甲]]。

2009年夏天，他轉執[[葡甲|葡甲]]球會{{scl|比拉馬}}的教鞭，這次更成功協助該隊升班至[[葡超|葡超]]。雖然渣甸在2010/11球季帶領球會[[護級|護級]]成功，但他在季尾卸任領隊一職<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-beira-mar-news/21495-jardim-steps-down-at-beira-mar|title=Leonardo Jardim steps down at Beira-Mar|publisher=PortuGOAL|date=28 February 2011|accessdate=29 May 2011|archive-date=2011-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110524001852/http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-beira-mar-news/21495-jardim-steps-down-at-beira-mar|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2011年5月，他代替過檔[[士砵亭|士砵亭]]的-{zh-cn:多梅戈斯·柏塞因西亚; zh-tw:多明戈斯·柏塞恩西亞; zh-hk:杜明高斯·柏仙尼亞}-（Domingos Paciência）出任{{scl|布拉加}}領隊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abola.pt/nnh/ver.aspx?id=264256|title=Pedro Martins: "Nélson Caldeira vai ser adjunto de Leonardo Jardim no SC Braga"|trans_title=Pedro Martins: "Nélson Caldeira will assist Leonardo Jardim at SC Braga"|publisher=[[A_Bola|A Bola]]|language=pt|date=20 May 2011|accessdate=29 May 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110523095226/http://www.abola.pt/nnh/ver.aspx?id=264256|archive-date=2011-05-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他帶領該會在2011/12球季取得第三名，更創造出聯賽15連勝之紀錄<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-braga-news/32309-lucky-13-for-braga|title=Lucky 13 for Braga?|publisher=PortuGOAL|date=26 March 2012|accessdate=4 June 2012|archive-date=2013-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017064101/http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-braga-news/32309-lucky-13-for-braga|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，但其後因與球會主席不和而離隊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.supersport.com/football/mozambique-portuguese/news/120531/Braga_rescinde_contrato_com_treinador_Jardim|title=Braga rescinde contrato com treinador Jardim|trans_title=Braga rescinds contract with coach Jardim|publisher=Super Sport|language=pt|date=31 May 2012|accessdate=4 June 2012|archive-date=2013-05-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6GslWHPLW?url=http://www.supersport.com/football/mozambique-portuguese/news/120531/Braga_rescinde_contrato_com_treinador_Jardim|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年6月5日，渣甸與[[希超|希超]]班霸[[奧林比亞高斯|奧林比亞高斯]]達成協議，簽約兩年<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ethnos.gr/ethnosport/article.asp?catid=8747&subid=2&pubid=129059818|title=Πέφτουν υπογραφές με Ζαρντίμ|trans_title=Jardim is signing|publisher=Ethnos|language=el|date=5 June 2012|accessdate=5 June 2012|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6GslbLx3F?url=http://www.ethnos.gr/ethnosport/article.asp?catid=8747|archive-date=2013-05-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>[http://www.footballcracy.com/news/europe/leonardo-jardim-to-be-olympiakos-new-coach/ Leonardo Jardim to be Olympiakos new coach] {{Wayback|url=http://www.footballcracy.com/news/europe/leonardo-jardim-to-be-olympiakos-new-coach/ |date=20120613182722 }}; Footballcracy, 8 June 2012</ref>。在翌年的1月19日，雖然球會在聯賽擁有10分的領先優勢，但他卻爭議性地與球會解約<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.olympiacos.org/en/article/19419/olympiacos-fc-statement|title=Olympiacos FC statement|publisher=Olympiacos' official website|date=19 January 2013|accessdate=25 January 2013|archive-date=2018-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181011063937/http://www.olympiacos.org/en/article/19419/olympiacos-fc-statement|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

渣甸於2013年夏天回國，與[[士砵亭|士砵亭]]簽約兩年<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2013-05-20/news/sns-rt-soccer-portugalsportingl6n0e1209-20130520_1_porto-and-benfica-leonardo-jardim-big-three-clubs|title=Soccer-Troubled Sporting appoint Jardim as coach|publisher=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]]|date=20 May 2013|accessdate=16 May 2014|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714150514/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2013-05-20/news/sns-rt-soccer-portugalsportingl6n0e1209-20130520_1_porto-and-benfica-leonardo-jardim-big-three-clubs|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他帶領這支由出產大量青訓球員的年輕球隊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/memberassociations/association=por/news/newsid=2007656.html|title=Jardim focused on bigger picture at Sporting|publisher=UEFA.com|date=9 October 2013|accessdate=16 May 2014|archive-date=2018-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181012014457/https://www.uefa.com/memberassociations/association=por/news/newsid=2007656.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-portuguese-abroad-news/42810-machado-qjardims-changed-sportingq|title=Paulo Machado: "Leonardo Jardim has changed the mentality at Sporting"|publisher=PortuGOAL|date=24 October 2013|accessdate=16 May 2014|archive-date=2013-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131106022747/http://www.portugoal.net/index.php/more-portuguese-abroad-news/42810-machado-qjardims-changed-sportingq|dead-url=yes}}</ref>取得聯賽亞軍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ionline.pt/artigos/desporto/leonardo-jardim-diz-nada-esta-decidido-na-luta-pelo-segundo-lugar|title=Leonardo Jardim diz que nada está decidido na luta pelo segundo lugar|trans_title=Leonardo Jardim says nothing is decided in fight for second place|publisher=IOnline|language=pt|date=3 April 2014|accessdate=16 May 2014|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303232726/http://www.ionline.pt/artigos/desporto/leonardo-jardim-diz-nada-esta-decidido-na-luta-pelo-segundo-lugar|dead-url=no}}</ref>，為這支[[里斯本|里斯本]]勁旅造出較去季多25分和18個入球的進步。

2014年6月10日，渣甸加盟[[法甲|法甲]]球會{{fc|摩納哥}}，合約為期兩年，並且附加一年浮動合約<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.asm-fc.com/en/article/leonardo-jardim-joins-as-monaco-65037.html|title=Leonardo Jardim joins AS Monaco|publisher=AS Monaco|date=10 June 2014|accessdate=19 June 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714185852/http://www.asm-fc.com/en/article/leonardo-jardim-joins-as-monaco-65037.html|archivedate=2014-07-14}}</ref>。摩納哥在班主的縮減開支下賣走多名主力球星如[[哈梅斯·罗德里格斯|-{zh-hans:哈梅斯·罗德里格斯;zh-hk:占士·洛迪古斯;zh-tw:哈梅斯·羅德里格斯;}-]]和[[法卡奧|法卡奧]]等等<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/sep/03/monaco-fans-refund-season-tickets-radamel-falcao|title=Monaco fans want refunds as Radamel Falcao and James Rodríguez leave|author=Guardian sport|work=the Guardian|accessdate=16 May 2015|archive-date=2019-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207113105/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/sep/03/monaco-fans-refund-season-tickets-radamel-falcao|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但渣甸仍將摩納哥打造成一支出色的防守型球隊，更帶領球會至2004年之後首次打入[[歐聯|歐聯]]八強<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/newsid=2223095.html|title=Monaco and Atlético squeeze into quarter-finals|date=18 March 2015|work=UEFA.com|accessdate=16 May 2015|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206193937/https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/newsid=2223095.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016/17球季，渣甸帶領年輕化的摩納哥殺入歐聯4強，是繼2003/04球季後再次達成此項成就。在聯賽方面，渣甸亦帶領摩納哥打破了PSG長達四年的壟斷，奪得了久違的法甲聯賽冠軍。

